{"tid":1782633,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企隻router有啲問題，換邊隻好？","createTime":"2019-12-14T06:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T06:43:58.000Z","uid":316802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6461b08de0099e62d6554d8fb4b9fcf9b050ae80","tid":1782633,"uid":316802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:37:10.000Z","msg":"屋企1000m上網，而家用緊ASUS rt-ac58u，發現佢5ghz WiFi得200mbps。咁我就做咗一輪速度測試，結果如下；<br />\n <br />\n電腦lan線插modem: 950mbps<br />\n電腦lan線插router(熄咗WiFi): 500-600mbps<br />\n電腦連接 5ghz WiFi: 180-200mbps<br />\n<br />\n已經check咗幾次電腦張無線網卡支援亦係連802.11ac<br />\n<br />\n個人判斷應該係router有問題，如果想wifi速度keep到至少500mbps以上，應該換邊隻好？"},{"pid":"3041ab5e7bbe149365fecdb914c37e8962b175cb","tid":1782633,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:39:53.000Z","msg":"N字頭"},{"pid":"31439d3f04f193bde06531a29a6c8f14ab007a64","tid":1782633,"uid":316802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3041ab5e7bbe149365fecdb914c37e8962b175cb","tid":1782633,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:39:53.000Z","msg":"N字頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:40:29.000Z","msg":"型號？"},{"pid":"d718d8aaddc4c8923b7323e919e95b772b355177","tid":1782633,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:43:57.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"25db2646882ca85c79558ced15f7b55bb3aa1f99","tid":1782633,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KcGJ4XB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKcGJ4XB.jpg&h=5b30d5fc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}